{"tid":2499924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共有風險，韓國一僑民在上海接種中國疫苗 3日後身亡","createTime":"2021-04-22T08:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T09:21:36.000Z","uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b93d5280187dbcc923c9a1cc7017c127cf4aad","tid":2499924,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:50:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">韓國一僑民在上海接種中國疫苗 3日後身亡</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/04/22 16:33<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北22日電）韓媒報導，<span class=\"red\">一名旅居中國上海市的韓國僑民，3天前在上海接種中國製的COVID-19疫苗後出現不適，這名40多歲韓僑今天上午在自家被發現身亡。9日，韓國駐上海總領事率先響應接種中國疫苗。</span><br />\n<br />\n韓聯社今天引述旅滬韓僑社區消息稱，這名韓僑19 日在上海的一家醫院接種中國醫藥集團研製的COVID-19 疫苗，此後出現噁心等異常反應。他並沒有基礎疾病。<br />\n<br />\n據韓聯社此前報導，<span class=\"red\">韓國駐上海總領事金勝鎬9日才在上海華山醫院接種中國藥企研製的COVID-19疫苗。</span><br />\n<br />\n據一名韓國駐中外交官透露，金勝鎬是首位接種中國國產疫苗的韓國外交官。<br />\n<br />\n金勝鎬於2020年底赴上海上任。今年2月，他在接受香港南華早報採訪時表示，他對中國研發的COVID-19 疫苗有信心，如果兩國政府相關部門決定給有意願的在中韓國人團體接種，自己會毫不猶豫地率先接種。<br />\n<br />\n4月9日，韓國駐上海總領事館網站刊發了金勝鎬在上海華山醫院接種疫苗的照片，並向醫護人員表示慰問和敬意。<br />\n<br />\n上海自3月29日起，根據「知情、自願、自費、風險自擔」原則，將在滬外籍人士中的適齡人群納入中國國產疫苗接種人群範圍，費用為每劑人民幣100元（約新台幣434元）。（編輯：楊昇儒/吳柏緯）1100422<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202104220223.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202104220223.aspx&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5Clnc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=7534dc24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202104220223.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"ec63336ec1e3d8d9c71cc6569be7f9cf9194e84c","tid":2499924,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">一旅滬韓僑接種新冠疫苗3天后身亡</span></strong><br />\n滾動 2021年 04月 22日 16:19<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社上海4月22日電 據旅滬韓僑社區22日消息，<span class=\"red\">3天前在上海接種新冠疫苗的一名40多歲韓僑A某當天上午在自家被發現身亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n據悉，A某19日在上海的一家醫院接種中國醫藥集團研製的新冠疫苗，此後出現噁心等異常反應。A某未患有基礎疾病。（完）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cb.yna.co.kr/gate/big5/img.yna.co.kr/etc/inner/CK/2021/04/22/ACK20210422004300881_01_i_P4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcb.yna.co.kr%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fimg.yna.co.kr%2Fetc%2Finner%2FCK%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2FACK20210422004300881_01_i_P4.jpg&h=936480a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片：圖為位於上海的一處外僑疫苗接種點。本圖片與報道內容無關。 韓聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cb.yna.co.kr/gate/big5/cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20210422004300881?section=search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcb.yna.co.kr%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fcn.yna.co.kr%2Fview%2FACK20210422004300881%3Fsection%3Dsearch&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5Clnc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=7aa972b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cb.yna.co.kr/gate/big5/cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20210422004300881?section=search</a>"},{"pid":"9f712266f409e832d6c80e800ced831403937a42","tid":2499924,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">詳訊：一旅滬韓僑接種新冠疫苗3天后身亡</span></strong><br />\n滾動 2021年 04月 22日 17:32<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社上海4月22日電 近日在滬接種新冠疫苗的一名南韓僑民22日被發現突然在家中死亡，目前尚未確定其死因是否與接種疫苗有直接關聯。<br />\n<br />\n據上海僑民社區和南韓駐上海總領事館等方面消息，<span class=\"red\">一名40多歲的南韓女性A某當天上午在家中被發現身亡。據悉，死者19日在上海同仁醫院接種中國國藥集團研製的新冠疫苗後出現噁心等症狀，其生前並無基礎疾病。</span><br />\n<br />\n上海總領事館方面表示，當地警方稱暫未發現他殺嫌疑，其家屬認為死因可能和疫苗接種有關。相關消息引發當地僑民不安，不少人取消接種計劃。（完）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cb.yna.co.kr/gate/big5/cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20210422006400881?section=search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcb.yna.co.kr%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fcn.yna.co.kr%2Fview%2FACK20210422006400881%3Fsection%3Dsearch&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5Clnc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=8eec7dd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cb.yna.co.kr/gate/big5/cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20210422006400881?section=search</a>"},{"pid":"e5a0c79370306bb57bdcb68430298a48233fd0bf","tid":2499924,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"死得好"},{"pid":"731dc531a68ab16eaf7339e3e58e8f32f930d17e","tid":2499924,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"投胎做中國人"},{"pid":"6f61ed8e323d74676a23fad86a6b9e86cce2f00c","tid":2499924,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"731dc531a68ab16eaf7339e3e58e8f32f930d17e","tid":2499924,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"投胎做中國人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f07ade1d6a4375be7b55bc9d9bfd312b41971f2","tid":2499924,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:14:31.000Z","msg":"願佢係地獄都可以瘋狂奶老毛"},{"pid":"e888611ec03bc101f2a7ceefb20a0647c9b09aac","tid":2499924,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/563/607410729670b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F563%2F607410729670b.jpg&h=361721c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ac88171dfcf2425cb2957bb48442898b08831ae","tid":2499924,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}